snippet.title: GTFO Rundown 8.0 Duality – Official Trailer (4K)
snippet.description:
The time is finally here. As just announced at @thegameawards, Rundown 8.0 Duality is out now! Bringing the story of the four prisoners to an end in the most GTFO way possible. 

This time is different/same. The right/wrong place with the wrong/right people. How low/high will you/they go before you start/stop following orders? This is the end/beginning.
